headline: Stocks are muted as Wall Street eyes Fed, Colgate-Palmolive upgrade
summary: Yahoo Finance Anchor Josh Lipton recaps three of the top stories on Wall Street, including investors waiting for the Federal Reserve's final rate cut decision of 2025, the latest analyst note on Colgate-Palmolive (CL), and Virgin Galactic (SPCE) reducing its debt. Stay up to date on the latest market action, minute-by-minute, with Yahoo Finance's Market Minute.
